snippet.title: Torchlight Frontiers | Railmaster Class Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign up for updates, exclusive content, beta tests, and more at https://www.TorchlightFrontiers.com 

Revealing the newest class to come to the frontier: Railmaster! A Railmaster relies on their powerful and customizable train. That and a really, really big hammer. Railmaster will make its debut in our ongoing Closed Alpha tests on April 23rd. Sign up for your chance to play at https://www.TorchlightFrontiers.com.

Torchlight Frontiers will be available on PC, Xbox One and PlayStation®4. 

Like: https://www.facebook.com/PlayTorchlight 
Follow: https://twitter.com/PlayTorchlight 
Watch: https://www.twitch.tv/PlayTorchlight
